>: </span><span class=\"english\">ফাল্গুন</span><span class=\"english\"> &gt; </span><span class=\"english\">ফাগুন</span><span class=\"english\">, </span><span class=\"english\">ফলাহার</span><span class=\"english\"> &gt; </span><span class=\"english\">ফলার</span><span class=\"english\">, </span><span class=\"english\">আলাহিদা</span><span class=\"english\"> &gt; </span><span class=\"english\">আলাদা</span><span class=\"english\">, </span><span class=\"english\">বাপজান</span><span class=\"english\"> &gt; </span><span class=\"english\">বাজান</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ইত্যাদি</span><span class=\"english\">।</span><span> </span></p><p><span class=\"english\">বিপ্রকর্ষ: </span><span class=\"english\">সময়</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">সময়</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">উচ্চারণের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">সুবিধার</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">জন্য</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">সংযুক্ত</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ব্যঞ্জন</span><span class=\"english\">- </span><span class=\"english\">ধ্বনির</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">মাঝখানে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">নতুন</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">স্বরধ্বনি</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">আসে</span><span class=\"english\">।</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">একে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বলা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">হয়</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">মধ্য</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">স্বরাগম</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বিপ্রকর্ষ</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">স্বরভক্তি</span><span class=\"english\">।</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">যেমন:</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">রত্ন </span><span class=\"english\">&gt; </span><span class=\"english\">রতন</span><span class=\"english\">, </span><span class=\"english\">ধর্ম </span><span class=\"english\">&gt; </span><span class=\"english\">ধরম</span><span class=\"english\">, </span><span class=\"english\">স্ব</span><span class=\"english\">প্ন </span><span class=\"english\">&gt; </span><span class=\"english\">স্বপন</span><span class=\"english\">, </span><span class=\"english\">হর্ষ </span><span class=\"english\">&gt; </span><span class=\"english\">হরষ ইত্যাদি</span><span class=\"english\">।</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">ধ্বনি-বিপর্যয়: </span><span class=\"english\">শব্দের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">মধ্যে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">দুটি</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ব্যঞ্জনের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">পরস্পর</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">স্থান</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">পরিবর্তন</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ঘটলে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">তাকে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ধ্বনি</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বিপর্যয়</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বলে</span><span class=\"english\">।</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">যেমন:</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ডেস্ক</span><span class=\"english\">&gt;</span><span class=\"english\">ডেক্</span><span class=\"english\">‌</span><span class=\"english\">স</span><span class=\"english\">, </span><span class=\"english\">রি</span><span class=\"english\">ক্</span><span class=\"english\">‌</span><span class=\"english\">সা</span><span class=\"english\">&gt;</span><span class=\"english\">রিস</span><span class=\"english\">্</span><span class=\"english\">‌</span><span class=\"english\">কা</span><span class=\"english\">, </span><span class=\"english\">পিশাচ</span><span class=\"english\">&gt;</span><span class=\"english\">পিচাশ</span><span class=\"english\">, </span><span class=\"english\">লাফ</span><span class=\"english\">&gt;</span><span class=\"english\">ফাল</span><span class=\"english\">, </span><span class=\"english\">তলোয়ার</span><span class=\"english\">&gt;</span><span class=\"english\">তরোয়াল</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ইত্যাদি</span><span class=\"english\">।</span></p><p><span> </span></p><p><span class=\"english\">নম্বর</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বণ্টন</span><span class=\"english\">:</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">অভিশ্রুতি, অন্তর্হতি, বিপ্রকর্ষ, ধ্বনি-বিপর্যয় প্রতিটির সঠিক সংজ্ঞা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">লেখার</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">জন্য</span><span class=\"english\"> ০১ </span><span class=\"english\">নম্বর</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">সর্বমোট</span><span class=\"english\"> ০৪ </span><span class=\"english\">নম্বর</span><span class=\"english\">।</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">অভিশ্রুতি, অন্তর্হতি, বিপ্রকর্ষ, ধ্বনি-বিপর্যয় প্রতিটির সঠিক উদাহরণ</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">লেখার</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">জন্য</span><span class=\"english\"> ০.২৫ </span><span class=\"english\">নম্বর</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">সর্বমোট</span><span class=\"english\"> ০১ </span><span class=\"english\">নম্বর</span><span class=\"english\">।</span></p><p><span> </span></p><p><span class=\"english\">প্রতি</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">২টি</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বানান</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ভুলের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">জন্য</span><span class=\"english\"> ০১ </span><span class=\"english\">নম্বর</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">কর্তন</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">হবে</span><span class=\"english\">।</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">বি.দ্র</span><span class=\"english\">. </span><span class=\"english\">পরীক্ষক</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ভুলগুলো</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">আন্ডারলাইন</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">অবশ্যই</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ঠিক</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">দিবেন</span><span class=\"english\">।</span></p>"
